    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty! It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it feels just like it did the day it rolled off the lot. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a new home, this is the one! I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
