    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade example of the high-revving S54 platform. Featuring the legendary 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies, the mechanical synchronization of the double-VANOS system is flawless. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers crisp, tactile engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. This chassis has undergone preventative subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive rod bearing service, ensuring structural integrity and longevity. The exterior retains its factory paint depth, while the undercarriage remains free of oxidation. A true driver\u2019s specimen with meticulous service documentation.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Zero accidents. Original paint and interior. Fully documented service history. Runs perfectly.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented in showroom condition, this vehicle is a true collector's dream. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero swirl marks or stone chips, recently treated with a professional-grade ceramic coating. Every body panel is perfectly aligned, and the factory alloy wheels are completely free of curb rash or oxidation. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of bolster wear, creasing, or fading, and the original carpets have been protected by floor liners since day one. All electronic components, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, function flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been exclusively maintained at authorized dealerships with a comprehensive service log included. It has been strictly garage-kept and never driven in inclement weather. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives as if it just left the factory floor.",
      "price": 48500.0,
