      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This vehicle reflects a level of care that transcends standard ownership, offering a pristine aesthetic and mechanical integrity synonymous with showroom delivery. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this acquisition represents a rare opportunity to secure a vehicle in peerless condition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
