    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely flawless condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells just like it did on day one. I\u2019ve babied it since the moment I got it, so it\u2019s running perfectly and looks stunning inside and out. You\u2019ve gotta see it to believe how clean it is! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44500.0,
