      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E92 M3, a superlative example of the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 era. This specimen is mechanically flawless, featuring a 6-speed longitudinal manual transmission and a Variable M Differential Lock for optimal torque vectoring. The vehicle is equipped with the Competition Package (ZCP), including a 10mm lowered chassis and remapped Electronic Damper Control (EDC) for surgical turn-in precision. Meticulously preserved with documented rod bearing prophylaxis and throttle actuator service. The carbon fiber reinforced plastic (CFRP) roof remains pristine, and the factory paint retains original depth. No track history; strictly garage-kept with a comprehensive service dossier. This is a turn-key investment for the discerning enthusiast seeking the pinnacle of atmospheric M-division engineering.",
